C1 and C2 are 30 pF adjustable capacitors.
For a radio mixer to work well, the reference oscillator level must be at least 10dB greater than the pitch oscillator level.
Now this is a theremin, not a radio, which imply the ration C1/C2 can be used to make wave shaping.
Keep also in mind than the lowest value of C1 and C2, the lowest will be the coupling between them and the possible lowest audio frequency.
